name: WKBackForwardList
desc: An object that manages the list of previously loaded webpages, which the web view uses for forward and backward navigation.

items.name: var backItem: WKBackForwardListItem?
items.desc: The item immediately preceding the current item, if any.

items.name: var forwardItem: WKBackForwardListItem?
items.desc: The item immediately following the current item, if any.

items.name: func item(at: Int) -> WKBackForwardListItem?
items.desc: Returns the item at the relative offset from the current item.

items.name: var backList: [WKBackForwardListItem]
items.desc: The array of items that precede the current item.

items.name: var forwardList: [WKBackForwardListItem]
items.desc: The array of items that follow the current item.
